9. Deterministic multi-signature orchestration

9.1 Signature set

{
  "requiredSigners": ["pk_1", "pk_2"],
  "collectedSignatures": [
    { "pubKey": "pk_2", "sig": "..." },
    { "pubKey": "pk_1", "sig": "..." }
  ]
}

9.2 Deterministic rule

sort(signatures by pubKey)
signatureHash = sha256(canonicalize(sortedSignatures))

Transition fires only if:

collectedSignatures == requiredSigners


